away from his snoring.

03:42.848 --> 03:45.224
Great. We'll have a girls night.

03:45.309 --> 03:46.475
No bras!

03:53.775 --> 03:56.861
Let's catch the tail
end of Nooky in New York.

03:57.154 --> 03:58.529
