who works on Wall Street.

04:20.469 --> 04:21.594
Broker?

04:21.678 --> 04:22.720
Nah, she's just really sore.

04:26.642 --> 04:29.060
This is so like our lives.

04:29.770 --> 04:32.271
It's like they hid a
camera in our apartment.

04:32.356 --> 04:35.232
Coming up next on BHO, it's Arli$$.

04:35.317 --> 04:36.609
Ah!

04:37.194 --> 04:38.653
Gentlemen, start your envy!

04:39.863 --> 04:43.157
Men's World Magazine has listed
the 100 richest men in the country,

04:43.241 --> 04:44.825
