04:44.910 --> 04:46.827
is Springfield native Artie Ziff.

04:46.912 --> 04:47.954
Ooh.

04:48.038 --> 04:50.289
Whoa! Your old boyfriend.

04:50.374 --> 04:52.375
Please. We went out once.

04:52.834 --> 04:55.795
