11:32.776 --> 11:35.486
And you get more
sprawl space on the bed.

11:35.612 --> 11:38.781
Wait. You really think Marge
is gonna fall for this guy?

11:38.865 --> 11:41.200
Even after I bought her
that hockey fight tape?

11:41.284 --> 11:43.202
I'd dump your ass. Me, too.

11:43.286 --> 11:45.037
Yeah, I can't get Artie out of my head.

11:45.121 --> 11:47.206
He's like a spy in the house of Moe.

11:47.290 --> 11:51.293
Oh, God, you're right. I gotta
get her back before it's too late!

12:00.553 --> 12:01.762
Hello, Artie.

12:02.847 --> 12:04.515
Where are you taking me?

12:04.599 --> 12:06.600
We're taking a trip through time.

12:06.768 --> 12:07.810
Forwards?

12:07.894 --> 12:08.936
No.

12:09.813 --> 12:12.689
Backwards! To the sexy '70s!

12:13.817 --> 12:17.277
Oh, my God! Artie, it's our senior prom.

12:20.490 --> 12:22.491
Burn, baby, burn

12:24.744 --> 12:26.328
I can't believe he's paying us

12:26.413 --> 12:29.123
a thousand bucks to
pretend it's the '70s.

12:29.207 --> 12:32.334
Disco Stu is working pro bono.

12:33.211 --> 12:37.881
Marge, many years ago I turned a
groovy night into a complete bummer.

12:37.966 --> 12:41.009
Tonight you get the
prom you always deserved.

12:41.511 --> 12:45.222
Precious and few are the
moments we two can share

12:45.306 --> 12:47.558
That's very sweet, Artie.

12:47.642 --> 12:49.476
Come, dear. We can dance all night.

12:49.769 --> 12:53.522
The band hasn't worked since
the wrap party for James at 16.

12:53.606 --> 12:55.566
Some say they're cursed.

13:06.953 --> 13:09.663
Oh, my God, it's our high school prom!

13:09.747 --> 13:11.707
And once again I have no date!

13:12.542 --> 13:13.625
Simpson!

13:13.710 --> 13:14.751
Hello, Dondelinger.

13:15.211 --> 13:17.838
You're not on the guest list,
Simpson. Orders of Prom King Ziff.

13:19.048 --> 13:20.090
And have you been drinking?

13:20.175 --> 13:21.967
Just for 25 years.

13:22.051 --> 13:23.343
Let's go, mister.

13:23.428 --> 13:24.720
Oh.

13:28.057 --> 13:30.934
You're very sweet, but no fake prom

13:31.019 --> 13:32.728
