peck on the cheek?

13:46.326 --> 13:47.409
Okay.

13:56.252 --> 14:00.756
Oh, no! If Marge marries
Artie, I'll never be born!

14:11.184 --> 14:13.310
Get off me, you little nerd!

14:16.940 --> 14:20.567
